{"tid":2455223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府訂購的阿斯利康疫苗，據德國$挪威科學家研究發現會導致血管堵塞！目前歐洲以多國停用！","createTime":"2021-03-21T02:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T09:32:13.000Z","uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"16d61243104d765e8b4ea3c41759d0942da28816","tid":2455223,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izUeFQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FizUeFQY.jpg&h=ce21034a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐洲多國已暫停接種阿斯利康新冠疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n據《華爾街日報》19日消息，德國和挪威的科學家表示，他們已確定阿斯利康疫苗與血栓報告之間的潛在聯系。兩個研究小組獨立發現該疫苗會引起自身免疫反應，引起抗體形成，它們進而再與血小板發生相互作用，導致大腦中產生血栓。<br />\n<br />\n挪威奧斯陸大學醫院血液學教授兼首席醫師霍爾姆（P&aring;l Andr&eacute; Holme）稱，&ldquo;這些人會產生這樣的免疫反應只能是疫苗原因。&rdquo;德國格賴夫斯瓦爾德大學診所輸血醫學教授格雷納徹（Andreas Greinacher）醫學博士表示，&ldquo;很少有人會出現這種並發症，&rdquo;&ldquo;但是，如果發生這種情況，我們現在知道如何治療患者了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n據CNN19日報道，在歐盟和英國，約有1700萬人接種了阿斯利康疫苗。《華爾街日報》報道指出，有30多名疫苗接種者被診斷出腦靜脈竇血栓，這些人中大多數是55歲以下的婦女。以上患者中有女性12名，有3人死亡。目前全球已有20多個國家暫停接種該疫苗。"},{"pid":"1c91017853096921d9dd99d6dcf5a7de0f51f6e9","tid":2455223,"uid":377617,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"港共訂既疫苗 冇一隻值得打 3隻都係搵命博"},{"pid":"64147f9bab5d8e8345a7413ba8f01eab545ab9eb","tid":2455223,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:46:04.000Z","msg":"出現血栓嘅位置好特别，唔係平時個 D。"},{"pid":"81a5bfba5bc8c3338ee8aae7d13d64979258c56d","tid":2455223,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:02:47.000Z","msg":"Oxford 枝針係EU 打左五百萬個人先有30 個有血管栓塞，英國自己都打左一千萬人都無咩大件事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bmj.com/content/372/bmj.n699\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2F372%2Fbmj.n699&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsffcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=410237a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bmj.com/content/372/bmj.n699</a>"},{"pid":"7baf80c60007658adeb3f0818f3ffdbe52d708a8","tid":2455223,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b301112c1b79a55881cb7eb89ca07eb7857d817","tid":2455223,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"無食早餐姐"},{"pid":"75d61c66c1e0414429724b233d8d5c7ed1686149","tid":2455223,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:41:43.000Z","msg":"連登仔力捧呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66049b85904ef5714fe047429f1e17dc6508eff","tid":2455223,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1c91017853096921d9dd99d6dcf5a7de0f51f6e9","tid":2455223,"uid":377617,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"港共訂既疫苗 冇一隻值得打 3隻都係搵命博"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:51:28.000Z","msg":"輝瑞最好 但一定唔會入貨 面子緊要人命"},{"pid":"963ee85385f1c0485168f6204329f8e02aae3b03","tid":2455223,"uid":48817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c66049b85904ef5714fe047429f1e17dc6508eff","tid":2455223,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1c91017853096921d9dd99d6dcf5a7de0f51f6e9","tid":2455223,"uid":377617,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"港共訂既疫苗 冇一隻值得打 3隻都係搵命博"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:51:28.000Z","msg":"輝瑞最好 但一定唔會入貨 面子緊要人命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"輝瑞咪biontech 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e5e23ae7fbefebf2e269209c333c82d11ecc13","tid":2455223,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c66049b85904ef5714fe047429f1e17dc6508eff","tid":2455223,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1c91017853096921d9dd99d6dcf5a